text: My wonderful urban planning students @ColumbiaGSAPP & I have assembled an annotated reading list on: Pandemic Urbanism: Praxis in the Time of COVID-19 <https://t.co/x7nyL5O8bm>. Our hope it'll be a collective effort “living document,"so pls. feel free to circulate/read/use/add.
